ion]] after winning 7 of 7 matches in tournament and beating Ukraine U21 in the final (3\u20131).<ref>[http://www.cev.eu/News.aspx?NewsID=23951&ID=10 ''Poland triumph with U20 European gold in Plovdiv''] \u2013 cev.eu \u2013 10-09-2016</ref> On July 2, 2017 [[Poland men's national under-21 volleyball team|Poland U21]], including Huber, achieved title of [[2017 FIVB Volleyball Men's U21 World Championship|U21 World Champion 2017]] after beating Cuba U21 in the final (3\u20130).<ref>[http://www.fivb.org/en/Volleyball/viewPressRelease.asp?No=69722&Language=en ''Poland shut out Cuba to triumph with U21 World Championship gold!''] \u2013 fivb.org \u2013 02-07-2017</ref><ref>[http://www.fivb.org/en/Volleyball/viewPressRelease.asp?No=69726&Language=en ''Great generation of Polish players crown time together with U21 world title''] \u2013 fivb.org \u2013 02-07-2017</ref> His national team won 47 matches in the row and never lost.<ref>[http://www.fivb.org/en/Volleyball/viewPressRelease.asp?No=69724&Language=en ''47 games without losing! I am so proud of these boys \u2013 coach Pawlik''] \u2013 fivb.org \u2013 02-07-2017</ref>\n\n==Sporting achievements==\n* '''National team'''\n** '''2016''' [[File:Gold medal europe.svg|16px]] [[2016 Men's U20 Volleyball European Championship|CEV U20 European Championship]]\n** '''2017''' [[File:Gold medal world centered-2.svg|16px]] [[2017 FIVB Volleyball Men's U21 World Championship|FIVB U21 World Championship]]\n** '''2019''' [[File:Bronze medal with cup.svg|16px]] [[2019 FIVB Volleyball Men's Nations League|FIVB Nations League]]\n** '''2019''' [[File:Simple silver cup.svg|16px]] [[2019 FIVB Volleyball Men's World Cup|FIVB World Cup]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{commons}}\n{{Poland men volleyball team 2016 CEV U20 European Championship}}\n{{Poland men volleyball team 2017 FIVB U21 World Championship}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Huber, Norbert}}\n[[Category:1998 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:People from Brzoz\u00f3w County